      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>This bill entitles a border patrol agent or Customs and Border Protection (CBP) officer who is assigned to a rural area through which illicit narcotics and undocumented aliens are routinely smuggled to hardship duty pay. </p> <p>The Commissioner of CBP shall designate such areas and establish the rate of hardship duty pay.</p>]]></text>
